<h2 id="expressions">Expressions</h2>

<ol>
  <li>
    <p>We shall be at Newcastle all the winter, and I dare say there will be some balls, and I will <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="take care to (do something)"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(确保做某事)</code></b> get good partners for them all.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>And then, you know, when once they get together, <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="there is no end of it"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(那事情可就没完了)</code></b>.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>“Oh! Certainly,” said Elizabeth, though <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="burning with curiosity (burning with - 心中充满情感、受...煎熬)"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(心中好奇不已)</code></b>, “we will ask you no questions.”</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>She then joined them soon enough to see Lydia, <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="with anxious parade (parade - 招摇/炫耀)"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(大摇大摆、迫不及待)</code></b>, walk up to her mother’s right hand.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>These parties were acceptable to all; to avoid <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="a family circle"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(家庭这个小圈子)</code></b> was even more desirable to such as did think, than such as did not.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>She had scarcely needed her present observation to be <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="satisfied"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(确信)</code></b>, from the reason of things, that their elopement had been brought on by the strength of her love rather than his.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>And there was my aunt, all the time I was dressing, preaching and <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="talking away (away在这里是一直、持续不断地意思)"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(喋喋不休)</code></b> just as if she was reading a sermon.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Well, Monday morning came, and I was <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="in such a fuss"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(担惊受怕)</code></b>!</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>However, <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="I did not hear above one word in ten"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(十句里面我最多听到了一句)</code></b>, for I was thinking, you may suppose, of my dear Wickham.</p>
  </li>
</ol>
